					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 90 sheep for a perpetual lamp with an <hi rend="italic">uḻakku</hi> of ghee every day in the temple of Tirukkaṟkuḍi-Paramēśvara by <hi rend="bold">Uḍaitalai Tirukkaṟkuḍi-Naṅgai</hi> wife of <hi rend="bold">Uḻaichchāṇaṉ Kaṇḍaṉ Śāttaṉ</hi> a resident of <hi rend="bold">Nandipanmamaṅgalam.</hi> This might be an inscription of <hi rend="bold">Uttama-Chōḷa.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
